---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Elevator Insights | Everest World Lifts Blog
description: Practical elevator planning, safety, maintenance, and modernization guidance from Everest World Lifts.
navKey: blog
heroCompact: true
heroTitle: Elevator Insights
heroText: Practical guidance for planning, maintaining, and improving vertical transportation systems.
heroImage: /assets/images/site/maintenance-technician.webp
---
{% include "components/hero.njk" %}

<section class="section-padding">
  <div class="container">
    {% if posts.length %}
      <div class="blog-grid">
        {% for post in posts %}
          <article class="blog-card">
            {% if post.imageUrl %}<a class="blog-card-image" href="/blog/{{ post.slug }}/"><img src="{{ post.imageUrl }}" alt="{{ post.imageAlt or post.title }}" loading="lazy"></a>{% endif %}
            <div class="blog-card-content">
              <p class="blog-meta"><span>{{ post.category or "Elevator insights" }}</span><time datetime="{{ post.publishedAt }}">{{ post.publishedAt | readableDate }}</time></p>
              <h2><a href="/blog/{{ post.slug }}/">{{ post.title }}</a></h2>
              <p>{{ post.excerpt }}</p>
              <a class="text-link" href="/blog/{{ post.slug }}/">Read article</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% else %}
      <div class="empty-state">
        <p class="eyebrow">Coming soon</p>
        <h2>We are preparing practical elevator guides</h2>
        <p>New articles will cover planning, safety, maintenance, accessibility, and modernization.</p>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Ask our team a question</a>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
